The U.S. Treasury said it will sell12.8 billion dlrs of three and six-month bills at its regularauction next week.    The March 30 sale, to be evenly divided between the threeand six month issues, will result in a paydown of 1.2 billiondlrs as maturing bills total 13.99 billion dlrs.    The bills will be issued April 2. Reuter&#3;